    "In contrast, LoRA merges its adapted matrices at the inference stage, thereby eliminating the need for extra memory beyond what is required by the original model.1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 66 68 70 72 74 Top-1 Accuracy (%) ImageNet 1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 68 70 72 74 76 Top-1 Accuracy (%) SUN397 1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 50 55 60 65 70 Top-1 Accuracy (%) DTD 1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 72 75 77 80 82 85 Top-1 Accuracy (%) UCF101 1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 20 25 30 35 40 45 50 55 Top-1 Accuracy (%) Aircraft 1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 55 60 65 70 75 80 85 90 Top-1 Accuracy (%) EuroSAT 1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 80 85 90 95 Top-1 Accuracy (%) Flower102 1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 83 84 85 86 87 Top-1 Accuracy (%) Food101 1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 90 91 92 93 Top-1 Accuracy (%) Pets 1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 93 94 95 96 Top-1 Accuracy (%) Caltech101 1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 70 75 80 85 Top-1 Accuracy (%) Cars 1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 67 70 72 75 77 80 82 Top-1 Accuracy (%) Average (ViT-B/16) 1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 62 65 67 70 72 75 77 Top-1 Accuracy (%) Average (ViT-B/32) 1 2 4 8 16 Number of shots 76 78 80 82 84 86 Top-1 Accuracy (%) Average (ViT-L/14) PLOT++ TaskRes Tip-Adapter-F CoOp ProGrad CLIP-LoRA How to apply LoRA for VLMs?In this section, we delve into the utilization of LoRA modules, identifying three principal design considerations: (1) the choice between tuning the vision encoder, the text encoder, or both, including the specific layers to adjust; (2) the selection of attention matrices for tuning; and (3) the determination of the appropriate rank for these matrices.We explore these aspects across three datasets: ImageNet, Stanford Cars, and EuroSAT.",
